Description_lang: Draw upon unholy and frost energies to become Undead for $d. While undead all damage is reduced by $m2% and you are nearly unstoppable becoming immune to Stun, Snare, Fear and Root effects.However, during Lichborne you cannot move faster than $s1% of normal speed.
AuraDescription_lang: Undead, and immune to Stun, Snare, Fear and Root effects.Damage taken reduced by $w2%.Unable to move faster than $s1% of normal speed.
